reviewText: Our kids loved it and now the grandson does too!
Had this movie before and loved it, dvd got messed up so I replaced it with this one, love this movie it is great for all ages.
Great children's movie that I enjoyed when I was little and now I can watch it with my own little one.

It's such a good movie, my daughter knew every word of it when she was a little girl. I bought it for her daughter, thinking it might be the same for her also. It's just a great thing, passing things down from one generation to another!

This was ordered for my niece, but my son (now 29) had watched it as a kid and then my younger son watched it as well. We love it.  Every time I hear Big Bird since "Blue Bird," I cry.  Silly, but it gets me every single time.  Arrived in less than a week after ordering with other items ordered, so very well pleased.

Wonderful movie for all ages. Great music, beautiful film production & a story that stands the test of time!
A must for every family collection.
Had this when my children were little.  Now a second generation is loving it!  What's not to love?  Good buy.
Grandson loves Big Bird. Good purchase.
Loved this movie as a child and now I get to share it with my toddler! Great family movie!
My kids loved this movie and all the singing. Bought it for my granddaughter. Enjoyable for us adults too.

Can't go wrong with the classic movie for kids that like/watch Sesame Street
Awesome movie when i was younger....Now my 4yr.old and 1yr.old love this movie!! They sing along to all the songs.so glad i found this movie and at an awesome price!

This is a classic film that every family should own.  The well known Sesame Street cast is present including all of the original muppets, Gordon, Olivia, Luis, Linda, etc.  Children will love the antics of Grover and Cookie Monster, the innocence of Big Bird, and the wonderful personalities that each of the characters bring to the film.  This film will have your kids loving Sesame Street for all of the same reasons you did when you were growing up and without all of the computer animated sketches on the program today.
